Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Thank you for speaking up for me last time, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: "I wasn't really able to do anything.", 3: '7', 4: "Don't you mind being called a fence sitter?", 5: '7'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "It is true that I'm neither here nor there, isn't it? Not to mention that there's only so much one person can do. That wasn't your fight, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I can't keep my role as a Purifying Force member away when I'm on the Gray Raven Task Force.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "And I can't tackle my missions like a proper Purifying Force member when I'm there.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "From what I can tell, I do seem to be sitting on the fence, don't I?", 4: '1'}
{2: "You're a remarkable member of my squad.", 3: '12', 4: 'But you managed to help a lot of people that way.', 5: '14'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Do you mean the people from the Support Force?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I didn't think they would thank me.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I wasn't forced into the Purifying Force because of my model, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "As I've told you, I don't intend to let the Purifying Force become a mindless coalition of butchers.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "That's why I've worked so hard to reach the position of leadership to make sure I know the story behind every case.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Even if I got called a fence sitter... I will still abide by my belief until the very end.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Just like what you did with me.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...The constant gifts and the little acts of intimacy, of course. Have you forgotten already, or have you...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Either way, you surely are fearless, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
